Alyeska Investment Group, L.P.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:01 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Alyeska Investment Group, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Alyeska Investment Group, L.P. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to corporations and other businesses. The firm manages a separate client focused portfolio. It also launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in equity and fixed income markets. The firm employs market neutral strategy to make its investments. It employs fundamental and quantitative analysis using long-short hedging strategies to make investments. Alyeska Investment Group, L.P. was founded in February, 2008 and is based in Chicago, Illinois.


77 West Wacker DriveSuite 700Chicago, IL 60601United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 312-899-7900

Fax: 312-899-7952

www.alyeskagroup.com







