Alyeska Investment Group Lp 

Share with your friendsYour NameYour EmailRecipient EmailEnter a MessageI read this article and found it very interesting, thought it might be interesting for you. The article is called Alyeska Investment Group Lp and is was published by Octafinance.com at http://www.octafinance.com/hedge-funds/alyeska-investment-group-lp/.CaptchaSubmitAlyeska Investment Group Lp is a Illinois-based hedge fund that was founded by Anand Parekh. It had more than $3.14 billion assets under management in March, 2014. Taken from Alyeska Investment Group latest Adv, the fund reported to have 28 full and part-time employees. Among which 19 performing investment advisory and research functions. The hedge fund had between 1-10 clients. Anand Parekh created Alyeska Investment Group in Chicago in 2008. The company follows a market neutral strategy taking both long and short positions. Alyeska managed $2.5-3 billion in 2011. Anand Parekh is a 38 year old from New Jersey and an avid runner.






